# Descipción larga, las lineas han de estar separadas por "\n "
longdesc: "This package contains the application and webpage that is showed on the first \n  Bardinux start."

# Versión del paquete
version: 1.0.5

# Cambios en esta versión
changes:
    - Added new box to the web to split privative and free extras.
    - Changed the size of page to adjust automatically.
    - Added preferences to get work apt url in app mode.
    - Changed the bardinux image and some colors.
